Developed a dynamic e-commerce website for a tile store using Python and Django.

Designed and implemented an interactive home page with product listings organized by category, subcategory, and individual items.

Implemented an admin module allowing staff to manage users, products, and vendors, facilitating easy addition and management of staff and vendors.

Integrated a robust purchase module to handle customer transactions, ensuring a smooth and secure purchase experience.

Implemented an order module to track and manage customer orders efficiently, providing a streamlined process for order fulfillment.

Designed and implemented a cart module, allowing users to add and remove items easily, enhancing the overall shopping experience.

Integrated a payment module, ensuring secure and seamless online transactions through various payment methods.
